<definition>
	<term id="scheme">scheme</term>
	<def>A systematic plan or arrangement for work, action, etc.</def>
</definition>
<definition><term id="scheme_entry">scheme entry</term>
	<def>An item in a scheme.
		<note>The item may correspond directly to an individual 
			action to be taken or 
			may represent a series of further scheme entries.
		</note>
		</def>
</definition>
